OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fnight with clear spells, although an
OL,7,Fisolated light shower is possible near
OL,8,Fto the east coast. Isolated low cloud
OL,9,Fand mist may form in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAny low cloud or mist will
OL,12,Fclear to leave plenty of fine weather
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells. However, there is
OL,14,Fpotential for an isolated shower to
OL,15,Fdevelop in places. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
