OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FThe
OL,6,Fweather should remain fine on Friday
OL,7,Fwith further spells of warm sunshine.
OL,8,FTurning cooler, breezier with the
OL,9,Fchance of rain at times through the
OL,10,Fweekend.
